title: ACI BGP peer entry
agents: special
catalog: hw
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 ACI BGP peer entry Check:
 '/api/class/bgpPeerEntry.json'

 There are configurable {{WARN}} and {{CRIT}} thresholds for the BGP drop rate.
 Also, if the operational status is 'idle', the check will become {{WARN}}. If the operational status is not 'established', it will become {{CRIT}}

inventory:
 All BGP peer entries the agent reports will be inventorized.

changelog:
 - initial version

